## Authority hierarchy

1. `docs/vision/VISION-LOCK.md`
2. ADRs in `docs/architecture/decisions/`
3. Architecture docs
4. Roadmap + phase plans
5. Open questions, tech debt
6. Instructions and prompts

Higher beats lower. Raise conflicts — never silently work around them.

## Self-modification

The builder does **not** edit its own instructions, prompts, or hook scripts during a phase. If a workflow improvement becomes obvious, append it to `## Proposed Workflow Improvements` in CURRENT-STATE and `docs/reference/agent-improvement-log.md`. Humans apply improvements between phases.
